headline: CFRA flags risks as Netflix is downgraded on WBD deal concerns
summary: Investing.com -- CFRA said in a note Monday that the outlook for Netflix has become more uncertain, with the firm downgrading the stock to Hold from Buy, citing rising risks tied to the company’s pursuit of Warner Bros. Discovery.
